title: Notice Was Returned To USCIS Because The Post Office Could Not Deliver It

Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Mailed To Me
body: On June 21, 2021, we mailed your new card for your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190151949, to the address you gave us. If you do not receive your card by July 6, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we send your new card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
